## COMPREHENSIVE CODEBASE EXPLORATION REPORT

### PROJECT STRUCTURE OVERVIEW
This is a small Express.js/TypeScript e-commerce API project with two main resource domains: Products and Orders. The architecture is currently characterized by business logic tightly coupled within route handlers, with in-memory data storage.

---

## 1. TEST FILES (COMPLETE CONTENTS & ANALYSIS)

