**Test Coverage Summary:**
- 7 tests total
- **GET /orders** (2 tests): Listing all orders, filtering by status, calculating summary stats (count, totalRevenue)
- **GET /orders/:id** (2 tests): Retrieving single order with item enrichment (product names), 404 handling
- **POST /orders** (3 tests): Creating orders, validating non-empty items, validating product existence, stock deduction
- **PATCH /orders/:id/status** (2 tests): Status transitions, enforcing valid state machine transitions

**Test Structure:**
- Uses **Supertest** for HTTP integration testing (not mocking, hitting the actual Express app)
- Uses **Vitest** as test runner
- Tests call route handlers via HTTP requests to the live app
- Tests rely on in-memory data state (shared across tests)

